modName: Warframe Soundtrack  We All Lift Together  Keith Power Replacer - DELETED
summary: this mod replaces the main menu music with the song from the Fortuna intro trailer for a new Warframe update.
descriptionHtml:
Credit to Keith Power for creating the song and Digital Extremes for creating the amazing ever evolving game that is Warframe.

lyrics:Â Cold, the air and water flowin' Hard, the land we call our home
Push, to keep the dark from comin'
Feel the weight of what we owe
This, the song of sons and daughters
Hide, the heart of who we are
Making peace to build a future
Strong, united, working til we fall
And we all lift
And we're all adrift together
Together
Through the cold mist
Til we're lifeless together
Together.





If anyone has any requests for songs they would like just leave it in a post, and on a side note when i get more time ill try to replace all of the skyrim sound track with the warframe ost i will also try to do requests for ost replacement aswell
